description:
Have you lost or found a pet in the Milwaukee, Wisconsin area? This page was created by PawBoost to help more fur babies get home safe & sound.
\
  nIf your pet is LOST, please report it here: 
https://www.pawboost.com/fb/milwaukee_wi

If you have FOUND a pet, please report it here:
https://www.pawboost.com/
fb/milwaukee_wi/found

Please LIKE this page so you can be in on the search when other cats, dogs, birds & other pets go missing near you :)

Here's what will ha
  ppen when you report a lost or found pet:
1. The lost or found pet will be posted to this page and go out to our followers. Be sure to comment on the post so that y
  ou will get notifications when there is a new comment.
2. Email alerts will go out to local members of the PawBoost network, which includes more than 35,000 vets, s
  helters, & volunteers across the country.
3. Your lost or found pet will be added to the PawBoost lost & found database, one of the largest lost & found pets databa
  ses on the web.
4. If your pet is LOST, you will be emailed a link where you can download a printable missing poster.
5. You will have the option to get the Facebo
  ok post in front of even more local people (not just this page's followers) by putting out a locally-targeted PawBoost Alert.

Best of luck!!
